Package: brainbox-cli
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Brainbox Team <support@brainbox.ai>
Depends: python3, python3-requests
Description: Brainbox CLI Linux log collection agent
 A lightweight Python daemon that collects logs, system metrics,
 and service status and sends the data to the Brainbox backend.
